name: Hand painting & forming porcelain workshop March 2014
description: For beginners and intermediates with Abby Seymour. x4 evening classes through March 2014 from 6pm - 9pm 4th, 11th, 18th, and 25th. Classes will be held In Abby's studio in Kensington, Melbourne, Australia. Come and learn, make and be guided through a porcelain project. These exclusive classes are limited to a small number of 10 students. Abby Seymour will be running classes based on her past years of experience working with porcelain. During the four classes you will be taught some of the basics about working with porcelain. The art of hand forming and hand painting on porcelain. You will come away with a couple of original pieces of jewellery made from scratch in porcelain, hand formed vessels or perhaps you have one of your own projects in mind that can be guided through. You will also get an insight into how to Abby creates her range or work.
